import { Link } from "react-router-dom"

const Signup = () => {
  return (
    <form className="form-control">
      <input 
      type="text"
      placeholder="Enter Name"
      />
      <input 
      type="password"
      placeholder="Enter Password"
      />
      <input 
      type="password"
      placeholder="Re-Enter Password"
      />
      <Link to="/">
      <input 
      type="submit"
      value="SignUp"
      />
      </Link>
    </form>
  )
}

export default Signup
